title: Select the POAP you like
body:
![楽しみにしています](https://gateway.pinata.cloud/ipfs/QmbBTXmStDQeYLJiqzVntjZUH1DZeNL6bMjp4GyrL8CpRF)
![闻いたこともねえ冒険が待ってるって言うんだぜ！](https://gateway.pinata.cloud/ipfs/QmeF5LhsxJU55amWybmQVLEkaSmRdA7xU131wstyxkfnMG)

The two above are POAPs that I have issued. The names are both in Japanese.

The first one is called "*楽しみにしています*", which means "**I'm looking forward to seeing you**".

The second one is called "*闻いたこともねえ冒険が待ってるって言うんだぜ！*", this is the last sentence before the death of pirate Roger in "One Piece", meaning "**The unheard of adventure is waiting for us**".

Select the POAP you like.
I will notify you in [Discord](https://discord.gg/7R6YwaZrx9) when it is available. Thank you!
choices: 闻いたこともねえ冒険が待ってるって言うんだぜ！
author: 0x1998e2AE038ef58948e3aB3F9ACDA84d2c2adf7e
